Package: pam-device-auth
Version: 0.3.2
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6, openssh-server (>= 1:9.6p1)
Conflicts: keycloak-ssh-auth
Replaces: keycloak-ssh-auth
Maintainer: Norbert Krucky <nk@dev.nk-it.cloud>
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/NK-IT-CLOUD/pam-device-auth
Description: SSH authentication via OIDC Device Authorization Grant (RFC 8628)
 PAM module for SSH login using any OIDC provider's Device Authorization
 Grant flow. Works headless. Supports Keycloak, Auth0, Okta, Authentik.
 Zero external Go dependencies.
